  "dialogue": {
    "11": {
      "id": "11",
      "speaker": "Gale",
      "text": "That hit the spot.",
      "context": "NodeContext: Brushing off the concern, not ready to talk about it",
      "checkflags": [],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "10",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "15": {
          "id": "15",
          "speaker": "Gale",
          "text": "I can feel it work. The magic is like a lullaby that sings to sleep the demon inside.",
          "context": "NodeContext: Brushing off the concern, not ready to talk about it",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "10",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "4": {
              "id": "4",
              "speaker": "Gale",
              "text": "A metaphorical demon I haste to point out. But no less dangerous - and no less bound to wake up again to continue its ravages. Such is the nature of all monsters.",
              "context": "NodeContext: Brushing off the concern, not ready to talk about it",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [
                "ORI_Gale_Event_ThankedForItem1_Global"
              ],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "10",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "18": {
                  "id": "18",
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I'm glad you're feeling better. Your condition sounds unpleasant, to say the least.",
                  "context": "NodeContext: Brushing off the concern, not ready to talk about it",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "10",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "16": {
                      "id": "16",
                      "speaker": "Gale",
                      "text": "Oh, it's not so bad once you get used to it. And on the plus side, my tower in Waterdeep has never been so free of clutter.",
                      "context": "NodeContext: Brushing off the concern, not ready to talk about it",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "10",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                },
                "1": {
                  "id": "1",
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "How do I know the real monster isn't you?",
                  "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale theatrically bows.\rNodeContext: Tongue-in-cheek, but the sentiment is sincere.",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "10",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "7": {
                      "id": "7",
                      "speaker": "Gale",
                      "text": "My words. My actions. My award winning smile.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "10",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                },
                "12": {
                  "id": "12",
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Perhaps now you'll tell me what all this is in aid of?",
                  "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale theatrically bows.\rNodeContext: Tongue-in-cheek, but the sentiment is sincere.",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "10",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "5": {
                      "id": "5",
                      "speaker": "Gale",
                      "text": "Grateful as I am, the course of our camaraderie is much better served by not taking that particular detour. Not just yet.",
                      "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale theatrically bows.\rNodeContext: Tongue-in-cheek, but the sentiment is sincere.",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "10": {
                          "id": "10",
                          "speaker": "Gale",
                          "text": "Sincerely though: I understand I ask a lot from you with few answers in return, but in time all will be told.",
                          "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale theatrically bows.\rNodeContext: Tongue-in-cheek, but the sentiment is sincere.",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "13": {
                              "id": "13",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "Don't mention it. I'm glad I could help.",
                              "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale theatrically bows.\rNodeContext: Tongue-in-cheek, but the sentiment is sincere.",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "0": {
                                  "id": "0",
                                  "speaker": "Gale",
                                  "text": "I bow to your boundless kindness.",
                                  "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale theatrically bows.\rNodeContext: Tongue-in-cheek, but the sentiment is sincere.",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": true,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "8": {
                              "id": "8",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "That condition of yours is a very expensive one.",
                              "context": "NodeContext: Tongue-in-cheek. He's in good spirits.",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "20": {
                                  "id": "20",
                                  "speaker": "Gale",
                                  "text": "I obtained it in Waterdeep. Nothing there comes cheap.",
                                  "context": "NodeContext: Tongue-in-cheek. He's in good spirits.",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": true,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "6": {
                              "id": "6",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "I hope we don't regret losing that artefact. It could have proven useful.",
                              "context": "NodeContext: He's in good spirits.",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "19": {
                                  "id": "19",
                                  "speaker": "Gale",
                                  "text": "I myself am a much more powerful artefact in your arsenal. Rest assured of that.",
                                  "context": "NodeContext: He's in good spirits.",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": true,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "3": {
                              "id": "3",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "Just so you know, this was the last time I part with such a valuable item.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "2": {
                                  "id": "2",
                                  "speaker": "Gale",
                                  "text": "I understand your reluctance, but to ignore my condition is to invite catastrophe.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "17": {
                                      "id": "17",
                                      "speaker": "Gale",
                                      "text": "Please, think on the matter. I trust that during our travels you'll navigate ample leagues of progressive insight.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": true,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {}
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                },
